data.description: This Home is like no other in the area with the quality & workmanship incomparable to other homes in this price range, appreciated by the most particular & selective. For full details, scroll through photos to see the List of Upgrades. Main Home is a 5,043 sq ft 4 bedroom 3 bathroom 2 1/2 Car Garage 2015 CBS construction w/Metal Roof, Impact Windows & Doors, SAFE ROOM with rebar, solid concrete poured columns, solid concrete ceiling & VAULT door. Saltwater Pool, PLUS a 2015 Detached CBS 62'x43' air conditioned 17' tall Building/Shop with Guest Apartment & Full Bathroom plus enough room to park 6 more vehicles! Shop has impact windows, interior stucco, custom compressed air system. The High end luxury features are just the beginning of what this property has to offer.
